timelineItems.text: Romain Gall looks ready to make his #Crew96 debut.

timelineItems.text: #Crew96 fans, watch out. Major hair about to check in in the form of Romain Gall.

timelineItems.comment: Offside, Columbus Crew. Romain Gall tries a through ball, but Aaron Schoenfeld is caught offside.

timelineItems.name: Brett Stewart
timelineItems.text: Solid wheels from Gall. I am already a fan! #Crew96

timelineItems.name: Daniel Andrews
timelineItems.text: First touch and.. wow @RomainGall #Crew96

timelineItems.name: Ryan Schwepfinger
timelineItems.text: This is what making your MLS debut looks like. #Crew96

timelineItems.comment: Attempt missed. Will Bruin (Houston Dynamo) right footed shot from outside the box is high and wide to the left. Assisted by Óscar García.

timelineItems.name: Andrew King
timelineItems.text: Oscar Garcia really yanked one there. Flew wide, but it had Clark beat. Pretty slow game thus far. #Crew96 #ForeverOrange

timelineItems.comment: Attempt missed. Jason Johnson (Houston Dynamo) left footed shot from long range on the right is close, but misses to the right. Assisted by Ricardo Clark.

timelineItems.name: Adam
timelineItems.text: #Crew96

timelineItems.comment: Foul by Aaron Schoenfeld (Columbus Crew).
David Horst (Houston Dynamo) wins a free kick in the defensive half.

timelineItems.name: Lydia Smith
timelineItems.text: I'm not used to seeing this score on the score board #Crew96 #IBelieveThatWeWillWin

timelineItems.name: matthewtkn
timelineItems.text: Pregame beer at the pub with club legend Frankie Hejduk, seats in the Nordecke & a 3-0 Crew W, now that's proper matchday experience #Crew96

timelineItems.name: Andrew King
timelineItems.text: Even though he's a man for the future, it's not hard to see why Berhalter is excited to work with Gall. So much spark to him.

timelineItems.name: Ben Ferree
timelineItems.text: I said 4 points from the last two home games would be stellar for this team. If 4 is stellar, is 6 cosmic? Get me a thesaurus. #Crew96

timelineItems.name: Sandeep Varry
timelineItems.text: That's two awesome weekends in a row. #Crew96! This can be our year! #MLS #ColumbusCrew

timelineItems.name: Dakota Stewart
timelineItems.text: WONDERFUL WIN! 3-0 Great job #Crew96

timelineItems.comment: Second Half ends, Columbus Crew 3, Houston Dynamo 0.
Attempt missed. Will Bruin (Houston Dynamo) right footed shot from outside the box is close, but misses to the right. Assisted by Ricardo Clark following a fast break.
